Excellent mushrooms here. I don't even know what all we ordered. Just pointed at a few things that sounded good and everything was good. Quite crowded, but at 21:30, more towards the end of the dinner hour, at least for that day, able to get a table with no wait. Main seating area is upstairs, so can't tell anything from just looking in.  Staff efficient and while somewhat curt, still friendly enough.
